Package com.i2group.apollo.itemstoreapi

Contains interfaces for simple interactions with the event bus and the item store from server-side code.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IItemAndSetRetrieval A pair of methods for retrieving Items and set contents from the item store, for use from implementations of IStatelessHandler.
IStatelessHandler A handler that receives Items and IEvents from the Intelligence Analysis Platform, and processes them statelessly.
